about.description:
LHS module for OpenTURNS
It provides optimized latin hypercube experiments

name: otlhs
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.3" %}

    - swig  # [not win]
    - openturns  # [not win]

  run:
    - python
    - openturns

about:
  home: http://openturns.org/
  dev_url: https://github.com/openturns/otlhs
  license: LGPLv3
  summary: Optimized LHS module
  description: |
    LHS module for OpenTURNS

extra:

    - jschueller
